{
  "texts": [
    "This creates networks or maps based on the data.",
    "Generated networks contain items or nodes representing objects of interest, such as authors, sources, countries, keywords, and lines that demonstrate the connection or relationship between them (every pair of items) in the form of co-citation and cooccurrence (van Eck and Waltman 2019).",
    "The strength of the individual links was designated as a positive numerical value.",
    "This relationship becomes stronger, corresponding to higher values.",
    "The sum of the times two items (e.g., authors) are quoted together indicates a link's strength."
  ]
}